Name: painter-tk
Version: 1.4.2.2
Summary: 使用tkinter的Canvas控件制作的画板程序, 支持编辑、保存文档以及文档属性等功能。 A painter using tkinter.Canvas, supporting editing and saving documents and modifying document properties, etc.
